name: Cats - A Nose Compose
description:
perfect noses, perfectly positioned

"Rule of thirds, wait, did you hear anything? Did you see anything? Do you see us? Perfect noses, perfectly positioned"

The composition of the cats' noses was made with the intention of expressing as much as possible the rule of thirds, where the noses of the two cats are located in two of the four thirds of the photo and in opposite positions.

- Loyalty
